      "text": [
        " أَمِيرُ اَلْمُؤْمِنِينَ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : «إِذَا لَمْ يَكُنْ لِلَّهِ عَزَّ وَ جَلَّ فِي اَلْعَبْدِ حَاجَةٌ اِبْتَلاَهُ بِالْبُخْلِ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1717 - The Commander of the Faithful Imam Ali ibn Abi Talib (as) said:\n\"If Allah (swt), the Mighty and Majestic, has no need for a servant, He tests him with miserliness.\""
        ]
      }
